msgid ""
"The purpose of this :fab:`github` Action is to preemptively test against the"
" **latest** resolved ``python`` variant of the :guilabel:`geovista-py3xx` "
"environment to uncover and highlight any issues prior to refreshing the "
":bash:`pixi.lock` file with the scheduled `ci-locks.yml`_ :fab:`github` "
"Action. See the packaging :ref:`tippy-gv-developer-packaging-continuous-"
"integration` section for further details."
msgstr ""

