#: ../../geovista/docs/src/developer/testing.rst:94
msgid ""
"Prior to running the tests ``pip`` installs the **latest** package "
"dependencies from the ``PyPI`` ecosystem. See the packaging :ref:`tippy-gv-"
"developer-packaging-python-package-index` section for further details."
