#: ../../geovista/docs/src/developer/testing.rst:97
msgid ""
"The purpose of this :fab:`github` Action is to preemptively test against the"
" **latest** resolved ``PyPI`` environment to uncover and highlight any "
"issues prior to the scheduled :fab:`github` `dependabot.yml`_ orchestrated "
"refresh of our ``PyPI`` package dependencies."
